---
title: Sesame Peanut Noodles with Bell Pepper and Carrot Ribbons
description: Pasta night just got a whole lot more fun (and delicious)! This takeout-inspired dish is all about minimal effort for maximal flavor—and it comes together faster than it takes to decide on which restaurant you’re ordering from. Twirly spaghetti is loaded with lightly charred bell pepper slices and carrot ribbons, then tossed in the World’s Most Delicious Sauce™. Peanut butter, sesame oil, lime juice, soy sauce, garlic, and ginger mingle to create a magical concoction so delicious and savory, you might just lick the plate. For a finishing touch, everything is showered in peanuts, toasted sesame seeds, and scallion greens. Creamy, crunchy, nutty goodness awaits!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/2019-w33-r8-sesame-peanut-noodles-2eb777bd.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/sesame-peanut-noodles-5d14d52f7ae20d000a65bebc-e6276f0b.pdf
servings: 2
course: main course
time required: 35 minutes
nutrition:
  calories: 900 kcal
  fat: 45 g
  saturated fat: 7 g
